a78b5fb1a2b6f60b401329cfd2d8349d4fdcc19628cde0e9b840b82e1a02e705f7d7413fe206aa13ed714ab93a65b62ac3d85dfd526ca8048621d5d89b22f0ef  musl-locale.patch"
